post.name: MOHAMMED EL MOUTAOUAKKIL
post.content:
#react #ai #interview #chatgpt3

Did you ever envision a future where you'd be answering questions from an AI interviewer? I certainly never did!

I asked chatGPT to act as an interviewer for a React js position, and here are some of the questions from the interview:

Can you explain what "lifting state up" means in React?
what does "unidirectional data flow" means in React?
Can you explain the difference between controlled and uncontrolled components in React?
Explain what the concept of "reconciliation" in React is and how it works.

Each time I answered, ChatGpt either answered by true or false and gave me the correct answer!

chatGPT is truly fascinating, give it a try, you'll be surprised!
